  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to investigate the association between metabolic syndrome (MS),
      body mass index (BMI), hyperglycemia, dyslipidemia, hypertension and thyroid cancer. Screen
      for the risk factors that affect the incidence of thyroid cancer.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
